NIGH to Newgate, on the Weſt-ſide of the Street, is St. Andrews Church. This is queſtionleſs the oldeſt Church of this Town, not only from it's


Situation, which is that Part where was principally the ancient Monkcheſter;
                     St. Andrew's Church. but alſo from the Model and Faſhion of it's building, it appearing in theſe Things older than the others.
